# SQLite is a derived artifact: rebuildable from the committed JSON snapshots
# via `pnpm restore`. We keep it out of git to avoid binary churn in history.
# The canonical, vendor-portable backup is data/json/ (committed).
data/officernd.sqlite
data/officernd.sqlite-*
data/*.sqlite
data/*.sqlite-shm
data/*.sqlite-wal
